# Text

## Summary

- Players can enter text
- Players see one text input during play
- Multiple configured answers are accepted alternatives for that one input
- Case sensitivity can be set per accepted answer
- Whitespace can optionally be ignored when checking the submitted text

## Use case

- Accept a short typed answer when spelling or wording matters
- Add several accepted alternatives when the same answer can be written in multiple ways
